# Keep the verdicts + reproducibility (paired_ab.json, records.jsonl, report.json,
# *.json certificates, *.sh, *.py, README.md, the small sweep_seed*.log arm markers)
# but never commit the multi-MB raw vLLM server logs / decode token dumps / clock
